WEBVTT

00:11:59.147 --> 00:12:00.548
from megafires.

00:12:00.572 --> 00:12:04.237
We all need to work together
to get this changed.

00:12:04.711 --> 00:12:06.672
And finally, there's managed wildfires.

00:12:06.696 --> 00:12:09.323
Instead of putting all the fires out,

00:12:09.903 --> 00:12:12.432
we need to put some of them back to work

00:12:12.456 --> 00:12:15.447
thinning forests and reducing dead fuels.

00:12:16.005 --> 00:12:18.672
We can herd them around the landscape

00:12:18.696 --> 00:12:20.609
when it's appropriate to do so

00:12:20.633 --> 00:12:24.536
to help restore the power
of the patchwork.

00:12:26.623 --> 00:12:30.362
And as you've probably figured out by now,